{
  "stem": "3820.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- there's no-- winters were hard, because as the clothes became worn, there was-- there was no new clothes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember that when I went to the farm, the-- I grew out of the clothes that I had brought with me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she made me-- my-- my parents had taken bedding into the forest, and they turned all this over to the people that I was living with.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she emptied one of the big pillows and made me a dress out of the-- the pillow cover, which was not-- was not the kind of pillow cases that we have here.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like a-- almost like a canvas material.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had no shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I ran around barefoot in the winter time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The closest thing I had to a shoe was like a Dutch clog with a wooden sole, and a little bit of leather on top.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that's about it for clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The first new dress I had was when my uncle took me to Kiev and got me a couple of dresses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall any to speak of, but there were illnesses due to malnutrition, due to-- there were-- I don't ever remember seeing a doctor in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If there was one, I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I got ill, or-- my mother-- you know, the mother takes care of the child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the colds, the things like that-- but I do not recall ever seeing a doctor in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because when he-- when my Uncle Chaim and my grandfather left the ghetto-- later my grandfather wasn't able to go, only my Uncle Chaim.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they went directly from the ghetto under escort to the German offices, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had never seen them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
